    "plan_content": "## Plan Summary\n\n**Root Cause:** Classic off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts`, line 7.\n\nThe loop condition in `processItems()` reads:\n```ts\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++)\n//                         ^^^^^^^^^ subtracting 1 skips the last element\n```\n\nThis makes the loop stop at index `length - 2`, never touching the final item.\n\n**The Fix — one character change:**\n```ts\n// Before (buggy)\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {\n\n// After (fixed)\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {\n```\n\n**Impact:** 3 of the 6 existing tests are currently failing because of this bug. After the fix, all 6 should pass.\n\nShall I go ahead and apply this fix?",
